------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                             Fighter Extras
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Name                               Description
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Huge weapons*                      Fighters have an innate ability to be more
                                   effective when using huge weapons.
                                   While using them, your accuracy may not be
                                   the greatest, but if you land a hit you're
                                   sure to do massive damage!

Shields*                           Fighters are able to attempt to block their
                                   opponents blows if they are using a shield.

                                   * Fighters are also able to wear a shield
                                     while using a 2-Handed or Huge weapon.

Berserk                            If you see a bard around, ask him to party!
                                   Bards have the ability to incite a berserk
                                   rage in you, thereby enhancing most of your
                                   abilities greatly!

Endurance                          Your endurance comes from your constitution,
                                   strength, wisdom, and dexterity.

Spell Points                       Your SP comes from your strength,
                                   constitution, and intelligence.
